OL,3,CRhondda Cynon Taf leader to step down
OL,4,Cafter 12 years
OL,6,FAndrew Morgan, the leader of Rhondda
OL,7,FCynon Taf Council, has confirmed he
OL,8,Fwill step down and will not seek re-
OL,9,Felection in 2027.
OL,11,FFirst elected in 2004, he is currently
OL,12,Fthe longest serving local government
OL,13,Fleader in the UK, but said "it was
OL,14,Ftime to seek new challenges".
OL,16,F"I am incredibly grateful for the
OL,17,Fopportunity I have had during this
OL,18,Ftime, to help shape and transform
OL,19,FRhondda Cynon Taf", he said.
