OL,3,CRhondda Cynon Taf leader to step down
OL,4,Cafter 12 years
OL,6,F"As someone whose career started as a
OL,7,Flocal government apprentice, I
OL,8,Frecognise the importance of local
OL,9,Femployment opportunities that the
OL,10,FCouncil provides".
OL,12,FThroughout his time in post, Mr Morgan
OL,13,Fled the council through the covid
OL,14,Fpandemic and severe flooding caused by
OL,15,FStorm Ciara and Dennis in 2020, and
OL,16,Fthen Storm Bert in 2024.
