OL,3,CRhondda Cynon Taf leader to step down
OL,4,Cafter 12 years
OL,6,FHe said: "It is only through the
OL,7,Fefforts and dedication of our staff
OL,8,Fthat my colleagues and I have been
OL,9,Fable to deal with the unprecedented
OL,10,Fchallenges we have faced during my
OL,11,Fperiod as a Leader."
OL,13,FIn June 2022, he was awarded an OBE in
OL,14,Fthe Queen's birthday honours for his
OL,15,Fpublic service and leadership during
OL,16,Fthe severe flooding in 2020, which
OL,17,Faffected more than 1,500 properties,
OL,18,Fhomes and businesses across the County
OL,19,FBorough.
