OL,3,CRhondda Cynon Taf leader to step down
OL,4,Cafter 12 years
OL,6,FBeyond his council duties, Mr Morgan
OL,7,Falso leads the Welsh Local Government
OL,8,FAssociation.
OL,10,FHe concluded by thanking his fellow
OL,11,FCouncillors for their support and said
OL,12,F"it has been a true pleasure and
OL,13,Fprivilege" to work alongside them.
OL,15,FThe Council's majority Group will
OL,16,Fshortly commence the process of
OL,17,Fselecting a new Group Leader.
